    public ResponseEntity<ConvertedDatatablesData<PlantSection>> PlantsItemPlantSectionsThymeleafController.datatablesByIdsIn(@RequestParam("ids") List<Long> ids, DatatablesColumns datatablesColumns, GlobalSearch search, DatatablesPageable pageable, @RequestParam("draw") Integer draw) {
        
        Page<PlantSection> plantSections = getPlantSectionService().findAllByIdsIn(ids, search, pageable);
        long totalPlantSectionsCount = plantSections.getTotalElements();
        ConvertedDatatablesData<PlantSection> data =  new ConvertedDatatablesData<PlantSection>(plantSections, totalPlantSectionsCount, draw, getConversionService(), datatablesColumns);
        return ResponseEntity.ok(data);
